        <!-- IMPORTANT DO NOT DELETE -->
        <div id='globe-graphic-container' style='height: 100%; overflow: hidden;'>
            
            <!-- (begin) graphic html here -->
            <h1 class='delta'>Vaccination exemption rates in kindergarten schools</h1>
            <div class='scene-maker buttons'></div>
            <div class='scene-maker container'>
                <div class='scene-maker scene'></div>
                <div class='scene-maker chatter iota'>
                    <div data-step='0' class='chatter hide'><span>Most kindergarten schools in Massachusetts have low vaccination exemption rates, including 480 schools with <span class='highlight zero'>100% vaccinated kids</span>. But that still leaves more than 400 schools with <span class='highlight some'>non-zero exemption rates</span>.</span></div>

                    <div data-step='1' class='chatter hide'></div>
                    <div data-step='3' class='chatter hide'></div>

                    <div data-step='2' class='chatter hide'><span>Schools with high exemption rates are peppered throughout the state. The highest: Hartsbrook School in Hadley, with 47% unvaccinated children.</span></div>
                </div>
            </div>
			<button class='btn btn--small btn--primary show-schools'>See town-by-town schools</button>
			<div class='towns hide theta'></div>
